{"type": "article", "id": 22454, "title": "这些化妆小物好用，纽约时装周的化妆间里全是", "description": "从发型到护肤、彩妆都有", "date": "2016-02-18T19:00:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 23582, "name": "美发梳"}, {"id": 23583, "name": "保湿乳"}, {"id": 23584, "name": "法国药妆"}, {"id": 23585, "name": "化妆棉"}, {"id": 23586, "name": "打底"}, {"id": 23587, "name": "脱妆"}, {"id": 15848, "name": "Evian"}, {"id": 23588, "name": "angle Teezer"}, {"id": 264, "name": "MUJI"}], "category": 19, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 702, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702152000Gbj12NC4ZaKvnftW.png", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">时装秀的后台化妆间，大概是很多人梦寐以求之地，那里有最专业的彩妆师、世界顶级（意味着最迷人的）超模，还有各个系列各个色号十分齐全的大牌彩妆产品。</p>\n<p class=\"\">英国的 Telegraph 最近“潜入了”纽约时装周一些品牌的后台，拍下了他们的化妆间都用了哪些产品。当然像 Muji 的化妆棉、依云（Evian）喷雾、贝德玛的卸妆水都不用介绍了。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021519478XUsSly2JqI7wVCv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151947rPWNLtIbuD5kizv7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>Embryolisse 保湿乳：</b></p>\n<p>法国药妆品牌 Embryolisse的保湿霜,其实就是支面霜，但是各大秀场后台都用它当妆前乳。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151948NYd6yP2bA0njp4ik.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151948q3iakUDXWQSCl4eA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.11226611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p>适合各种肤质，保湿效果好并且不油腻，所以不容易脱妆、浮粉。Telegraph 说这也是支分分钟卖光的货。平时都是白色管的，去年 65 周年庆推出了金色的限量包装。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151949A2eZSnECBVvlwTMi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p><b>Tangle Teezer 美发梳：</b></p>\n<p>在女装品牌 Herve Leger  的秀场后台，据知名发型师（还有“美国最贵发型师”之称） Orlando Pita 介绍，这一场秀的头发造型要异想天开、好玩，但同时也要整齐。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151949ZFfXmELj071k2xDI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070215195027OQ3vGiXHxUJudB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68341709\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p>这就要用到前些年就特别火的美发梳 Tangle Teezer，其借助部分弯曲及长短不一的梳齿设计，达到柔顺的效果，甚至说能梳开一切打结的头发。宣传的噱头是“凯特王妃的最爱”，好莱坞明星和超模们也有不少人使用。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151951r08eLtIQy5OBn1vU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68055556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><b>Heritage Store  玫瑰水：</b></p>\n<p>为 Tory burch、ALEXANDER WANG 等品牌负责秀场彩妆的知名美妆师 Diane Kendal，不止在一个场合推荐了这款喷雾。在为那些超模化妆之前会用上它做保湿的准备，有收缩毛孔、保湿使妆容服帖的功效。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151952MCa5Up2ZuDTO3hg0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151952hr1exPVaCUTkqdzg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p><b>Beauty Blender 海绵：</b></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151953OZ34uATdfDIvmbqG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151953rVqbUzsi3t51QL4k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p>俗称“美妆蛋”，由美国化妆师Rea Ann Silva 研发，是设计成立体水滴形状、有一个尖端的海绵上妆工具。<a href=\"http://www.beautybay.com/accessories/beautyblender/sponge?utm_source=google%2Bshopping&amp;amp;utm_medium=organic&amp;amp;utm_campaign=shopping%2Bfeed&amp;amp;selectedSku=BEBL0001F&amp;amp;ctyid=gb&amp;amp;gclid=CMbste6f_MoCFdQaGwodlikDfw\">售价 21.6 美元</a>，在 Diane von Furstenberg 的后台随处可见。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021519542bVlIF5d9SApzc7f.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151955wPk2MhmI7l4oVNaF.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49814815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Diane von Furstenberg 本次的秀</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">美妆博主也爱用这个来打底，大头用来大面积铺匀底妆，尖的一头则用在鼻翼、眼角等细节处。并且比一般的海绵密度大，不会浪费粉底液，上妆效果服帖。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>Elmer 紫色胶棒（ Disappearing Purple Glue Stick）：</b></p>\n<p class=\"\">这个挺有趣的，<a href=\"https://www.stuff4crafts.com/elmer-s-washable-school-glue-stick-purple-3-pkg-77oz-e562.html?currency=GBP&amp;amp;CAWELAID=120018150000023826&amp;amp;gclid=CLjv5qig_MoCFcvpwgod1A8Mdg\">很便宜（2.75 英镑三支</a>）的胶棒却被用来了化各种妆。拧开是紫色的膏体，涂上去干了之后会变无色透明，有美妆博主在 YouTube 上用这个来去黑头——鼻子上涂一层干了之后揭掉。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151956t3aV6kIS0iNyUm9G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151957pyCvaBR43X5xHndk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.06666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">而 <a href=\"http://www.vogue.com/fashion-shows/fall-2016-ready-to-wear/jeremy-scott/slideshow/collection#8\">Jeremy Scott 本次的秀</a>，超模们的脸颊上粘着星星做装饰，都是用这支可水洗且不伤害皮肤的胶棒。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151958CsIBuLH3xRdmUZwN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151959CZEQYGAnr8WsSJPj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">题图来自：<a href=\"http://coralsandcognacs.com/2013/09/behind-the-scenes-at-targets-fall-fashion-show.html\">coralsandcognacs.com</a> </p>\n\n"}